{"tid":1465894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已到抗爭分差路，懇請每位抗爭者行動前好好思考梁天琦呢番話","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:32:55.000Z","uid":172454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"afb1bbd24e1cc33ceaa2bf181d1064ef8c3a06bf","tid":1465894,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"真正的公義還未來臨，你們或許因而心中充滿憤怒，這乃是人之常情。<br />\n但我懇請你們<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不要被仇恨支配自己</span></strong>，在危難中，仍要時刻保持<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警覺與思考</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n我們必須<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">警惕每一言一行</span></strong>，到底會更<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">接近目標</span></strong>，還是<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">距離更遠</span></strong>呢？<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好為左一時既「勝利」，放棄抗爭初衷，付出整個香港既未來作代價。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"29091f958a2d3ca8c7e93f600b6a2cd40a3b3c45","tid":1465894,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:26:33.000Z","msg":"今日真係太唔冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7e6f8fc393db2b34e0a7d74d5e77fe37b3d1da","tid":1465894,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:32:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命！"}]}